ttps://rescuethemes.com/wordpress-themes/culinary/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Culinary</a>, <a href=\"https://themegrill.com/themes/colormag/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ColorMag Pro</a>, <a href=\"https://themegrill.com/themes/accelerate/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Accelerate Pro</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Lucille</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Lucille is a beautifully designed WordPress theme, suitable for musicians, artists, music bands, producers or anyone working in the music industry.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/lucille-music-wordpress-theme/19078867\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Lucille</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Culinary</h2>\n<blockquote><p>A Free WordPress Theme for Food and Recipes</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://rescuethemes.com/wordpress-themes/culinary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Culinary</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">ColorMag Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Magazine WordPress theme. Suitable for news, newspaper, magazine, blogging kind of sites.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themegrill.com/themes/colormag/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase ColorMag Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Accelerate Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Accelerate is best suitable for small-medium businesses. Also, suitable for clean personal blog site.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themegrill.com/themes/accelerate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Accelerate Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=RKiG1aK2sYY:Q9xnUcUe-2o:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=RKiG1aK2sYY:Q9xnUcUe-2o:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=RKiG1aK2sYY:Q9xnUcUe-2o:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=RKiG1aK2sYY:Q9xnUcUe-2o:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=RKiG1aK2sYY:Q9xnUcUe-2o:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=RKiG1aK2sYY:Q9xnUcUe-2o:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/RKiG1aK2sYY\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://wpml.org/2018/04/wpml-compatible-themes-