f website demos that fits almost every niche. Additionally, it is bundled with a custom version of Visual Composer. Salient offers a rich and easy-to-use theme options panel which facilitates controlling how your website looks like. It is also worth mentioning the Salient is WooCommerce ready.</p>\n<p>Salient theme integration with WPML wouldnâ€™t have been possible without the cooperation of Theme Nectar team.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Salient-theme-and-WPML.gif\"><img src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Salient-theme-and-WPML.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"618\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1544892\" /></a></p>\n<p>We have created a detailed tutorial that explains <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/create-multilingual-wordpress-websites-using-the-salient-theme-and-wpml/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">building multilingual websites using Salient theme and WPML</a>. </p>\n<p>The integration allows you to translate the different textual elements using the Translation Editor.<br />\n<figure id=\"attachment_1544893\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme.png\"><img src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"462\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1544893\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme.png 1284w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme-150x99.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme-300x198.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme-768x508.png 768w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-translation-editor-with-Salient-theme-1024x677.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Translate Salient using the WPML Translation Editor</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>Need any help with you Salient multilingual website? Check the list of <a href=\"https://wpml.org/contractors/?wpv_view_count=1435673&#038;wpv-wpcf-how-big-projects-can-you-handle=&#038;wpv-wpcf-do-you-provide-maintenance=+&#038;wpv-site-theme%5B%5D=salient&#038;wpv-wpcf-how-small-projects-can-you-take=\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">the official WPML contractors</a> who specialize in building and maintaining sites built using the Salient theme.   </p>\n<p>If your building a multilingual website using the Salient theme and WPML, share your experience with us in the comments section below.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=QWEOlPXWHgc:5JpdSrKMBzw:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=QWEOlPXWHgc:5JpdSrKMBzw:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=QWEOlPXWHgc:5JpdSrKMBzw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=QWEOlPXWHgc:5JpdSrKMBzw:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=QWEOlPXWHgc:5JpdSrKMBzw:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=QWEOlPXWHgc:5JpdSrKMBzw:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/QWEOlPXWHgc\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://wpml.org/2018/04/salient-theme-and-wpml-are-officially-compatible/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comm