:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:326:\"Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins. The plugins are: Borlabs Cache, WP Multi Store Locator Pro If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3363:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-995848\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png\" alt=\"Compatible Plugins-Header\" width=\"400\" height=\"121\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header-150x45.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Compatible-Plugins-Header.png 680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins.</p>\n<p>The plugins are: <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/borlabs-cache-wordpress-caching-plugin/20194541\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Borlabs Cache</a>, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/wp-multi-store-locator-pro/19385351\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WP Multi Store Locator Pro</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Borlabs Cache</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WordPress Caching plugin</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/borlabs-cache-wordpress-caching-plugin/20194541\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Borlabs Cache</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WP Multi Store Locator Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin provides a number of options for admin in backend to manage their stores and sales manager for respective franchise.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/wp-multi-store-locator-pro/19385351\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase WP Multi Store Locator Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=_y40JmMSnTU:NYLEeh_EF1k:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=_y40JmMSnTU:NYLEeh_EF1k:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=_y40JmMSnTU:NYLEeh_EF1k:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=_y40JmMSnTU:NYLEeh