le-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png\" alt=\"compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image.png 568w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-150x42.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Compatible-woocommerce-extention-header-image-300x84.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /><br />\nToday we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible WooCommerce extensions.</p>\n<p>The WooCommerce extensions are: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/weight-country-woocommerce-shipping/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce Shipping Pro with Table Rate</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ti-woocommerce-wishlist/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">TI WooCommerce Wishlist</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/disable-downloadable-repeat-purchase/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Disable Downloadable Repeat</a>, <a href=\"https://fluxcheckout.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flux Checkout</a>, <a href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/stock-synchronization-for-woocommerce/19425704\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Stock Synchronization for WooCommerce</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and are ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">WooCommerce Shipping Pro with Table Rate</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Define multiple shipping rates based on weights and countries.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/weight-country-woocommerce-shipping/\" target=\"_blank\">Download WooCommerce Shipping Pro with Table Rate</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">TI WooCommerce Wishlist</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Add a user whichlist to your WooCommerce store</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ti-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\">Download TI WooCommerce Wishlist</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Disable Downloadable Repeat Purchase</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This WooCommerce plugin prevents a user from being able to purchase a downloadable product that they already own.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/disable-downloadable-repeat-purchase/\" target=\"_blank\">Download Disable Downloadable Repeat Purchase</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Flux Checkout</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Mobile Checkout Plugin For WooCommerce</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://fluxcheckout.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Flux Checkout</a></p>\n</div\n\n\n\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Stock Synchronization for WooCommerce</h2>\n<blockquote><p>synchronizes the stock information from a CSV file to the WooCommerce inventory.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/stock-synchronization-for-woocommerce/19425704\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Stock Synchronization for WooCommerce</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=_8W55ngMy7E:ndvQTNmUhgE:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=_8W55ngMy7E:ndvQTNmUhgE:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=_8W55ngMy7E:ndvQTNmUhgE:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=_8W55ngMy7E:ndvQTNmUhgE:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=_8W55ngMy7E:ndvQTNmUhgE:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=_8W55ngMy7E:ndvQTNmUhgE:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/_8W55ngMy7E\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-mar-2018/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/compatible-woocommerce-extensions-mar-2018/\";s:7:\"at