compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Panarea</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce compatible theme with many options especially focused on restaurants and food in general.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/panarea-restaurant-and-food-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Panarea</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fashionair</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://weblizar.com/themes/fashionair-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Fashionair</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BuildPress</h2>\n<blockquote><p>BuildPress is customizable WordPress theme suitable for construction and building business.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.proteusthemes.com/wordpress-themes/buildpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase