"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/d2uSrOcTO2c/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/build-multilingual-news-websites-using-newspaper-theme-wpml/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 15 Mar 2018 10:55:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=1544936\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:360:\"The Newspaper theme is one of the top used themes among our clients to build magazine and news websites. Newspaper is flexible and highly customizable. It is bundled with Revolution Slider and WPBakery Page Builder to facilitate the process of designing your pages. Additionally, it comes with the tagDiv Composer, a visual drag-and-drop page builder [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4410:\"<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1547526 size-large\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1-1024x435.png\" alt=\"wpml newspaper\" width=\"1024\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1-1024x435.png 1024w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1-150x64.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1-300x128.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1-768x326.png 768w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Slice-1.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a><br />\nThe <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/newspaper/5489609\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Newspaper theme</a> is one of the top used themes among our clients to build magazine and news websites. Newspaper is flexible and highly customizable. It is bundled with Revolution Slider and WPBakery Page Builder to facilitate the process of designing your pages. Additionally, it comes with the tagDiv Composer, a visual drag-and-drop page builder that offers custom design elements and many grids. Not to mention that the Newspaper theme offers a huge number of pre-built templates.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In collaboration with tagDiv team, we managed to make the Newspaper theme and WPML fully compatible. Check our detailed guide on <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/create-multilingual-wordpress-websites-using-the-newspaper-theme-and-wpml/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">building multilingual websites using the Newspaper theme and WPML</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Newspaper-and-WPML.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1544965\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Newspaper-and-WPML.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"462\" /></a></p>\n<p>The integration allows you to translate all the Newspaper theme elements using the Translation Editor.<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1544982\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1246\" height=\"687\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor.png 1246w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor-150x83.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor-300x165.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor-768x423.png 768w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/The-WPML-Translation-Editor-1024x565.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1246px) 100vw, 1246px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We interviewed Radu Oprea, the co-founder of tagDiv about the Newspaper theme and how it became so popular. Check out the interview <a href=\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/interview-building-news-websites-with-wpml-newspaper-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>Need any help with you Newspaper multilingual website? Check the list of <a href=\"https://wpml.org/contractors/?wpv_view_count=1435673&amp;wpv-wpcf-how-big-projects-can-you-handle=&amp;wpv-wpcf-do-you-provide-maintenance=+&amp;wpv-site-theme%5B%5D=newspaper&amp;wpv-wpcf-how-small-projects-can-you-take=\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">official WPML contractors</a> who specialize in building and maintaining sites built using the Newspaper theme.</p>\n<p>Already building multilingual news website using Newspaper theme and WPML? Share your experience with us in the comments section below.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=d2uSrOcTO2c:wmYOboW5vvs:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=d2uSrOcTO2c:wmYOboW5vvs:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=d2uSrOcTO2c:wmYOboW5vvs:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=d2uSrOcTO2c:wmYOboW5vvs:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=d2uSrOcTO2c:wmYOboW5vvs:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=d2uSrOcTO2c:wmYOboW5vvs:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/d2uSrOcTO2c\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/build-multilingual-news-websites-using-newspaper-theme-wpml/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/build-multilingual-news-websites-using-newspaper-theme-wpml/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"Interview â€“ Building news websites with WPML &amp; Newspaper theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/XNTsgMMJG-0/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/interview-building-news-websites-with-wpml-newspaper-theme/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 12 Mar 2018 03:34:55 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Case studies\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=1543005\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:355:\"To learn more about how to build a news website using the WordPress CMS platform, Iâ€™ve contacted tagDiv, a best-seller theme author. I spoke with Radu Oprea, the co-founder of tagDiv, and also the senior developer behind the Newspaper WordPress theme. Â  WPML &#8211; How does Newspaper help clients to build news-related websites? Radu Oprea: [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Marine Larmier\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9181:\"<h2>To learn more about how to build a news website using the WordPress CMS platform, Iâ€™ve contacted tagDiv, a best-seller theme author. I spoke with Radu Oprea, the co-founder of tagDiv, and also the senior developer behind the Newspaper WordPress theme.</h2>\n<h3>Â <a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tagdivofficial.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1546726 size-large\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tagdivofficial-1024x568.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"568\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tagdivofficial-1024x568.png 1024w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tagdivofficial-150x83.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tagdivofficial-300x166.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tagdivofficial-768x426.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></h3>\n<h2><b>WPML &#8211; How does Newspaper help clients to build news-related websites?</b></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<h3>Radu Oprea:</h3>\n<p>&#8220;When you are designing a news website, you realize you need a complex structure that stays minimal at the same time, with clean and modern layouts, ad areas for monetization, advanced filters for content, and much more. All that can be accomplished as quickly as possible without any coding knowledge involved, as tagDiv has designed all the settings you may need for your website and integrated them in a fast, highly-optimized WordPress theme. Every grid, every block, and every module has been created to help users build a news website in no time.</p>\n<p>The tagDiv Composer is the first page builder ever created for online newspapers and magazines. With their content and Newspaperâ€™s architecture, it almost doesnâ€™t matter what website they are planning to build, as this theme is up to the task.&#8221;</p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Indeed, you have different layouts available and you can classify articles as â€œmost popularâ€ or â€œrecent stories,â€ while also showcasing many other articles by custom categories such as Health, Gadgets, Vogue, or Travel:</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1755739\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/image5-e1524457678798.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-1755739 size-full\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/image5-e1524457678798.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"463\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Categories classification</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Monetize your site thanks to the multiple locations for display advertising:</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<figure style=\"width: 739px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/NT5x9-y21xQORDL6-90j2y0e-KlgfOqriIQxAvwbalVWPBGDRcncY7igXF_WGI2Bga83Ihl0CBejtEn4-FcQSEPNY3eBN9JGn38g9BgLnC7JzTEQtR-mYtiUHhnmJSZKLQ8HuZGLK0EizaTiBg\" alt=\"\" width=\"739\" height=\"729\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Advertising space</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Sharing tools are integrated for each post (over 37 social sharing buttons available):</h3>\n<figure style=\"width: 687px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/9rfFMvzcbOVT5QjKY1MXdfTP5c_ghSkW3a18OyqDdxj5yEDIDZGpmmLgfP8dinKqUSIzBxQdEJ0_Bwz5wgdEAyOSg1KPbOwmsQklLru0BkjnuT0ix-YxUUjMf1AGZ26qINMH37Ox3tM3aJ2zNA\" alt=\"\" width=\"687\" height=\"315\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sharing Tools</figcaption></figure>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>You can write reviews and use stars or percentages to summarize results as shown below:</h3>\n<figure style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/FX8JAq3zhzPXjCls8rOT3oNo02ibpZ9BxoJnvcpyt60Wgc7_eqZSPfifV_zxSgCIqN1NrR1Pmd1EczkvATNAiDmjyu-cWNXC-VJKcl24OaCqYxEm-vOG-2TNToYkbzO9EA5ITgjHQhBzCXoFNQ\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"639\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Reviews: stars and percentage</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>With the Mega Menu feature , you can add custom categories, pictures, or font to the menu:</h3>\n<figure style=\"width: 787px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/hf-utcKzmW-Uf_qUra7F_NR-tekGMr6AEORxgePhFEs9Sd6uo0DoAz1y6WEIc0ZW6gfad1MOXhDvPn1IylrK-x7NpbYttzgzQ7zQO02svgAbPYxLotKvqDI5ruK8hwxF5_vV7B_H_oSAq4gnYA\" alt=\"\" width=\"787\" height=\"331\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mega Menu features</figcaption></figure>\n<h3>Build smart lists such as â€œtop 10 things to do in the USA.â€ A slider format is also available:</h3>\n<figure style=\"width: 478px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/hX_xNLBNnO1rDmOywKMDvN2CEa8QD7KZKiWtmBm5XDUlai3Xjubs-8ZHosZmrnpBKHiXUYvFkAlpn43dC-c-3dS3IMK1NgherFZj3ikrjEKN_hKPADMTzmTNXoEInmzHUaMMIrkB_1z6cGzQUA\" alt=\"\" width=\"478\" height=\"833\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Smart list</figcaption></figure>\n<h2><b>WPML &#8211; What makes Newspaper a &#8220;must have&#8221; theme?</b></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<h3>Radu Oprea:</h3>\n<p>&#8220;Newspaper is a fast loading theme and the best choice for high-traffic websites. Clients put their trust in Newspaper because itâ€™s continuously improved. Every problem that may occur is quickly fixed. Developers learn from their users and strive to make the best template even better.</p>\n<p>Newspaper is an easy-to-use and intuitive theme that has all the features you may need in the publishing industry. Letâ€™s put it this way: with this theme, you donâ€™t have to be a web developer, a designer, or an experienced publisher to create and manage a successful online magazine. You simply donâ€™t need coding skills to use this template.</p>\n<p>The customer support is at high standards with a dedicated team ready to help and advise clients in every stage of the website building process. The <a href=\"https://tagdiv.com/about-us/)\">tagDiv system</a> <a href=\"https://forum.tagdiv.com/newspaper-theme-documentation/\">also provides comprehensive documentation</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yCoy4jbfoEA&amp;list=PL6CsDkMaejhr2ExZCO73U11SSVKB9r_NE&amp;index=1\">professional video tutorials</a>. &#8220;</p></blockquote>\n<hr />\n<h2><b>Five good reasons to translate your news website with WPML: </b></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Reach an international audience and gain new readers.</li>\n<li>Build trust amongst your new readers, as they are more likely to trust a company who writes in their native language. Itâ€™s called the â€œcultural comfort zone.â€</li>\n<li>Show that you are an open-minded company willing to think, work, and write globally.</li>\n<li>Differentiate your news site from your competitors.</li>\n<li>Get a SEO boost.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2><b>Testimonial &#8211; Marek Stacho, multilingual website owner &#8211; Livinator.comÂ </b></h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Marek Stacho</td>\n<td>Testimonial &#8211; Founder of <a href=\"https://livinator.com/\">Livinator.com</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/marek-e1520825579551.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1543039\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/marek-1024x1016.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1016\" /></a></td>\n<td><i>&#8220;Newspaper was my first choice for Livinator.com when I founded the website back in 2014. I searched through hundreds of different WordPress templates, but only Newspaper was offering me all the functionalities I wanted. Livinator.com is offering content in two languages &#8211; English as the primary and Czech as secondary. Today, I can have every field translated and thanks to the combination of Newspaper and WPML plugin. I can run only one installation of WordPress with one database. Until now I was struggling and had to have two separate instances &#8211; each residing under a different domain name. There is no better solution for a responsive, multilingual website, which is running fast and reliably under one database. Luckily I do not have to spend any time on configuration anymore; I am only enjoying how smoothly everything works&#8221;.</i></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Are you planning on developing a news website with different languages? <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/create-multilingual-wordpress-websites-using-the-newspaper-theme-and-wpml/\">Use our documentation about Newspaper theme and WPML</a> and tell us how it goes!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=XNTsgMMJG-0:57kaNaAZMCs:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=XNTsgMMJG-0:57kaNaAZMCs:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=XNTsgMMJG-0:57kaNaAZMCs:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=XNTsgMMJG-0:57kaNaAZMCs:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=XNTsgMMJG-0:57kaNaAZMCs:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=XNTsgMMJG-0:57kaNaAZMCs:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/XNTsgMMJG-0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"https://wpml.org/2018/03/interview-building-news-websites-with-wpml-newspaper-theme/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssna