ble themes. The themes are: Shout, Deasil, Fixology If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3725:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-975307\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png\" alt=\"WPML Compatible themes\" width=\"400\" height=\"112\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several WPML compatible themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are: <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/shout-blogging-wordpress-theme/20161880\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Shout</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/deasil-wordpress-theme-for-travel-and-tour-agency/20480110?s_rank=1\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Deasil</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/fixology-handyman-multiservice-wordpress-theme/20901357\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Fixology</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Shout</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Blogging WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/shout-blogging-wordpress-theme/20161880\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Shout</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Deasil</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Travel and Tour Booking WordPress Theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/deasil-wordpress-theme-for-travel-and-tour-agency/20480110?s_rank=1\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Deasil</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fixology</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Handyman Multi-Service WordPress Theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/fixology-handyman-multiservice-wordpress-theme/20901357\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Fixology</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=DOC3i64sgmQ:vfIGHyP3lko:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.